## ğŸ¯ **Overview**

Crypto markets constantly shift between structural regimes such as:
- Panic crashes  
- High-volatility turbulence  
- Trend-following momentum  
- Low-volatility mean reversion  

This project implements a **modular ML framework** for:
- Hidden Markov Models (HMM)
- Gaussian Mixture Models (GMM)
- Bayesian Change Point Detection (CPD)
- Feature-rich market state analysis
- Walk-forward evaluation

